snippet.title: Touhou 3 - Phantasmagoria of Dim. Dream - Lunatic 1cc - Marisa - Stage 1-4
snippet.description:
Aka a run without a "broken" character.
PoDD's lunatic is often seen as the hardest in the series to 1cc... with a high-tier character.
So you can imagine how it's like without a high-tier character.
The real threat in this game are the bosses. Cancelling them out with a level 4 spell is a must strategy.

Stages 1 and 2 went fairly well. Although I was playing like a retard in stages 3 and 4.
